canfigger
------------------------------------------
Simple configuration file parser library

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.7-1
  libcanfigger-devel-0.3.1-1bl1
  libcanfigger0-0.3.1-1bl1
  pkg-config-2.5.1-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.46-1
  cygport-0.37.7-1
  gcc-core-13.4.0-1
  meson-1.6.1-1
  ninja-1.13.2-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/andy5995/canfigger

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/andy5995/canfigger/archive/refs/tags/v0.3.1.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack canfigger-0.3.1-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./canfigger-0.3.1-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/canfigger-0.3.1-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/canfigger-0.3.1-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libcanfigger0-0.3.1-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libcanfigger-devel-0.3.1-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

